<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 10:08:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Ben-Gvir 在以色列报纸上刊登广告，指责 Shin Bet 首席执行官“10 月 7 日失败”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-runs-ad-against-shin-bet-chief-for-failing-on-october-7-in-israeli-newspapers/00000191-888c-d460-abd3-f88e74460000</link><description>该广告包括 Ben-Gvir 党 Otzma Yehudit 的标志，并描绘了 Shin Bet 主席 Ronen Bar 的照片，声称他“在 10 月 7 日失败了，正在带领以色列走向另一场灾难”。对鲁莽的交易说不。首相办公室尚未回应</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-runs-ad-against-shin-bet-chief-for-failing-on-october-7-in-israeli-newspapers/00000191-888c-d460-abd3-f88e74460000</guid></item><item><title>从庇护所到聚会，这些是以色列公众在真主党威胁下的指导方针</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/from-shelters-to-gatherings-the-guidelines-for-the-israeli-public-amid-hezbollah-threat/00000191-88c5-dd90-a7d1-cbffc5970000</link><description>以色列后方司令部宣布了针对 30 个地区中 14 个地区居民的新准则，其中包括大特拉维夫地区、整个加利利地区和大海法地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/from-shelters-to-gatherings-the-guidelines-for-the-israeli-public-amid-hezbollah-threat/00000191-88c5-dd90-a7d1-cbffc5970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部被爆炸装置炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-by-explosive-device-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000191-8868-d1a4-abbf-896ed2670000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，阿米特·萨迪科夫上士的死亡是自10月7日战争爆发以来第700名士兵死亡，也是自几周后以色列军队进入加沙以来第367名士兵阵亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 08:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-by-explosive-device-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000191-8868-d1a4-abbf-896ed2670000</guid></item><item><title>尽管真主党升级，以色列代表团仍将前往开罗参加加沙协议谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/despite-hezbollah-escalation-israeli-delegation-to-leave-for-gaza-deal-talks-in-cairo/00000191-8836-d460-abd3-f8362f460000</link><description>尽管人们越来越怀疑其是否有能力取得突破，但仍决定派遣代表团参加开罗峰会，这可能表明以色列认为周日黎巴嫩边境的暴力升级已经结束</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 07:16:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/despite-hezbollah-escalation-israeli-delegation-to-leave-for-gaza-deal-talks-in-cairo/00000191-8836-d460-abd3-f8362f460000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列监狱长在监狱里探望了杀害巴勒斯坦家庭的凶手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prisons-chief-reportedly-visited-palestinian-familys-murderer-in-prison/00000191-85fc-dda4-a7ff-d5fed8550000</link><description>据报道，以色列监狱管理局局长科比·雅科比 (Kobi Yaakobi) 和伊塔马尔·本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben-Gvir) 的幕僚长查纳梅尔·多夫曼 (Chanamel Dorfman) 至少曾到监狱探望过阿米拉姆·本·乌利尔 (Amiram Ben-Uliel) 一次。 Ben-Uliel 因 2015 年用燃烧弹谋杀 Dawabsheh 家族而被判三项无期徒刑，正在服刑</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 05:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-prisons-chief-reportedly-visited-palestinian-familys-murderer-in-prison/00000191-85fc-dda4-a7ff-d5fed8550000</guid></item><item><title>真主党表示，在以色列国防军先发制人地袭击了数千个黎巴嫩目标后，真主党结束了“第一阶段”报复行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article-live/idf-launches-wave-of-lebanon-strikes-as-israel-braces-for-major-hezbollah-escalation/00000191-8715-d632-add9-b7778aa50000</link><description>以色列国防军周六公布在加沙阵亡士兵姓名 ■ 以色列国防军相信真主党想要针对情报部门、摩萨德基地 ■ 以色列代表团将于周日前往开罗进行协议谈判 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：三人死亡；基础设施受损</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 04:15:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article-live/idf-launches-wave-of-lebanon-strikes-as-israel-braces-for-major-hezbollah-escalation/00000191-8715-d632-add9-b7778aa50000</guid></item><item><title>美国试图防止局势升级，以色列准备在未来几天内应对真主党的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-for-hezbollah-attack-in-coming-days-as-u-s-seeks-to-prevent-escalation/00000191-8605-d847-abff-efaf31cf0000</link><description>开罗会谈几乎没有取得任何进展，因为加沙和以色列北部的局势持续升级，内塔尼亚胡坚持以色列在费城路线沿线的存在，这违背了国防机构的建议</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 23:06:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-for-hezbollah-attack-in-coming-days-as-u-s-seeks-to-prevent-escalation/00000191-8605-d847-abff-efaf31cf0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，最新的停火提议排除了以色列在埃及-加沙边境的永久存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-latest-deal-proposal-excludes-permanent-israeli-presence-on-egypt-gaza-border/00000191-85e7-dd90-a7d1-cfffd2a10000</link><description>该计划将允许内塔尼亚胡宣布以色列将继续留在费城路线，直到找到替代方案。 预计埃及会将这一版本交给已宣布参加开罗峰会的哈马斯</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 20:42:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-latest-deal-proposal-excludes-permanent-israeli-presence-on-egypt-gaza-border/00000191-85e7-dd90-a7d1-cfffd2a10000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯兰国声称对德国造成三人死亡的袭击负责：“为巴勒斯坦穆斯林报仇”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-24/ty-article/islamic-state-claims-attack-in-germany-that-killed-three-to-avenge-muslims-in-palestine/00000191-85de-d79a-a9fd-e5ff824a0000</link><description>警方表示，袭击者在斯洛尼根的一个节日上割断了多人的喉咙，造成三人死亡、至少八人受伤，其中四人伤势严重。伊斯兰国声称对此负责，称其目的是“为巴勒斯坦和世界各地的穆斯林报仇”</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 19:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-24/ty-article/islamic-state-claims-attack-in-germany-that-killed-three-to-avenge-muslims-in-palestine/00000191-85de-d79a-a9fd-e5ff824a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，三名以色列预备役士兵在加沙地带中部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-battle-in-the-central-gaza-strip-idf-announces/00000191-859e-d79a-a9fd-e5ff97cc0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布中士。丹尼尔·佩切纽克 (Danil Pechenyuk) 少校，26 岁，中士。尼泰·梅托迪 (Nitai Metodi) 少校，23 岁，周五在加沙城 Zeitoun 社区发生的爆炸中丧生。在另一起事件中，中士。亚尼夫·伊扎克·奥伦 (Yaniv Itzhak Oren) 少校，35 岁，在加沙中部的战斗中身亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 19:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-reserve-soldiers-killed-in-battle-in-the-central-gaza-strip-idf-announces/00000191-859e-d79a-a9fd-e5ff97cc0000</guid></item><item><title>蒙面以色列定居者在不同事件中袭击了巴勒斯坦西岸的两个村庄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-settlers-attack-two-palestinian-west-bank-villages-in-separate-incidents/00000191-8560-d03f-a1bd-ff6d4f0f0000</link><description>周六，蒙面定居者在巴勒斯坦西岸村庄发动袭击，造成至少两人受伤并损坏财产。截至周六晚上，尚未逮捕任何人</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 18:11:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-settlers-attack-two-palestinian-west-bank-villages-in-separate-incidents/00000191-8560-d03f-a1bd-ff6d4f0f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 323 天：哈马斯代表团前往开罗了解谈判最新情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-323-hamas-delegation-heads-to-cairo-for-update-on-negotiations/00000191-8518-d179-a995-cd78664b0000</link><description>哈马斯代表团将抵达开罗，了解停火/人质谈判的最新情况；哈马斯：并不意味着他们会参加会谈 ■ 周日的峰会包括中央情报局局长、美国中东问题特使布雷特·麦格克、卡塔尔总理、埃及情报部门负责人以及以色列情报部门负责人 ■ 黎巴嫩从黎巴嫩向以色列发射了 100 多枚火箭弹 ■以色列国防军：部队在拉法加沙市打死数十名恐怖分子 ■ 法国犹太教堂附近疑似纵火袭击中警官受伤 ■ 战争进入 323 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 17:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-323-hamas-delegation-heads-to-cairo-for-update-on-negotiations/00000191-8518-d179-a995-cd78664b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙卫生部称，周六加沙有近 70 人死亡、200 多人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/close-to-70-killed-over-200-wounded-in-gaza-on-saturday-gaza-health-ministry-says/00000191-851c-d03f-a1bd-ff3db4eb0000</link><description>以色列军队撤出加沙南部城市哈马德的某些地区后，卫生官员发现了数十具尸体。返回的居民回忆道：“什么都没有，没有公寓，没有家具，没有房屋，只有破坏”</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:43:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/close-to-70-killed-over-200-wounded-in-gaza-on-saturday-gaza-health-ministry-says/00000191-851c-d03f-a1bd-ff3db4eb0000</guid></item><item><title>开罗峰会前夕，以色列呼吁内塔尼亚胡达成停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-cairo-summit-israelis-call-for-netanyahu-to-make-a-cease-fire-deal/00000191-84ac-d179-a995-cdec7abd0000</link><description>“看来这是最后的机会了。人质的母亲说，要么达成协议，要么事态升级。人质被绑架到加沙十多个月后，每周都有抗议活动敦促达成协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 16:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/on-eve-of-cairo-summit-israelis-call-for-netanyahu-to-make-a-cease-fire-deal/00000191-84ac-d179-a995-cdec7abd0000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院检察官呼吁对以色列和哈马斯官员的逮捕令做出紧急裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/icc-prosecutor-calls-for-urgent-ruling-on-arrest-warrants-for-israeli-and-hamas-officials/00000191-848c-d632-add9-b5ffd64e0000</link><description>在一份法庭文件中，检察官卡里姆·汗敦促法官就他对以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡、哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔等人发出逮捕令的请求做出裁决</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 14:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/icc-prosecutor-calls-for-urgent-ruling-on-arrest-warrants-for-israeli-and-hamas-officials/00000191-848c-d632-add9-b5ffd64e0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫因厄立特里亚政治发生争吵，两名厄立特里亚人死亡，多人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/two-eritreans-killed-multiple-wounded-in-tel-aviv-brawl-over-eritrean-politics/00000191-848a-dcc6-a5bf-b5cf57950000</link><description>据称，袭击者刺伤多人，并向教堂投掷催泪瓦斯，造成包括儿童在内的多名成员受伤。特拉维夫警察局长称这种情况“不可接受”，并呼吁将袭击者驱逐出境</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 14:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/two-eritreans-killed-multiple-wounded-in-tel-aviv-brawl-over-eritrean-politics/00000191-848a-dcc6-a5bf-b5cf57950000</guid></item><item><title>周五从黎巴嫩向以色列发射100多枚火箭弹，两栋房屋遭到直接击中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/over-100-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-at-israel-on-friday-two-houses-suffer-direct-hit/00000191-8348-d445-a39f-dfe9f4ab0000</link><description>周五，以色列北部多处地点因黎巴嫩发射的火箭弹而起火 ■ 以色列国防军袭击了黎巴嫩的多个目标，造成至少七名真主党特工死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 07:58:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article/.premium/over-100-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-at-israel-on-friday-two-houses-suffer-direct-hit/00000191-8348-d445-a39f-dfe9f4ab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备应对真主党的重大升级，以色列国防军对黎巴嫩发动一波袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article-live/rockets-from-lebanon-hit-two-homes-in-northern-israeli-city-of-kiryat-shmona/00000191-8250-d00c-a7fd-b656dcb70005</link><description>哈马斯卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 40,334 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙被杀。 ■ 以摩萨德负责人为首的以色列代表团将于周日前往开罗参加停火谈判。 ■ 美国高级将领未经宣布进行中东之行，将于下周 ■ 以色列国防军呼吁加沙地带中部几个街区的居民撤离 ■ 法国警方正在搜寻涉嫌纵火袭击犹太教堂的嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 03:18:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-24/ty-article-live/rockets-from-lebanon-hit-two-homes-in-northern-israeli-city-of-kiryat-shmona/00000191-8250-d00c-a7fd-b656dcb70005</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦青少年在下班时被以色列狙击手射杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-teen-was-getting-off-work-when-he-was-shot-dead-by-an-israeli-sniper/00000191-811e-d03f-a1bd-fb3f86330000</link><description>沙迪正在他父亲的洗车场工作，一群年轻人开始从附近的校园向边境警察投掷燃烧弹。一名狙击手从远处向他们开枪，未击中并杀死了沙迪</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 22:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-teen-was-getting-off-work-when-he-was-shot-dead-by-an-israeli-sniper/00000191-811e-d03f-a1bd-fb3f86330000</guid></item><item><title>仅有海峡还不够：伊朗希望用新型无人机航母出海</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/the-straits-are-not-enough-iran-wants-to-take-to-the-oceans-with-a-new-drone-carrier/00000191-7e84-d8d0-a7bb-ffa570590000</link><description>伊朗在中东培养真主党和其他傀儡民兵，使其能够控制对全球贸易至关重要的关键水道。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 19:11:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-23/ty-article/.premium/the-straits-are-not-enough-iran-wants-to-take-to-the-oceans-with-a-new-drone-carrier/00000191-7e84-d8d0-a7bb-ffa570590000</guid></item></channel></rss>